Toy zone data

Source: R/data.R
toy_zones.Rd

Note that this dataset requires the sf package to work properly. This dataset contains 11 SA2 zones of Melborune CBD, Australia in a sf::sf format.

toy_zones

Format

A sf::sf data frame with 11 rows and 14 variables:

zid

(integer()) zone id

sa2_main

(integer())

sa2_5dig11

(character())

sa2_name11

(character())

sa3_code11

(character())

sa3_name11

(character())

sa4_code11

(character())

sa4_name11

(character())

gcc_code11

(character())

gcc_name11

(character())

ste_code11

(character())

ste_name11

(integer())

albers_sqm

(double())

geometry

(list())
